Questions
In the table, what descriptions would you assign to the Home rows?
On Windows OS, is fs::path_home() relevant at all to R administration?
Do ppl ever manually change/redirect fs::path_home() or fs::path_home_r()? Or are those just always left as default?
Should the paths have forward or backward slashes?
Should I leave the paths as-is with username and work specific info, or modify to make more generic?
Why do sometimes file paths get abbreviated with tildes? Like C:\PROGRA~1\R\R-41~1.2
Any other feedback!
TL;DR
